{{Top|leg}}
Located in [[Montrol City]] on [[Gandle Ott]], the '''Theatre Danske''' was a huge, multi-balconied building with wooden railings and red drapes. During the visit of the crew of the ''[[FarStar]]'' to Gandle Ott, the theatre staged a performance of ''[[Madra Teene]]''. During a performance, an [[Assassin droid/Legends|assassin droid]] attempted to eliminate senior members of the crew of the ''FarStar'' who were attending the show at the time. The assassin droid was destroyed in the fighting.

